com.rscja.deviceapi

类 RFIDWithISO15693

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rscja.deviceapi.RFIDWithISO15693

  • public class RFIDWithISO15693
extends java.lang.Object
    RFID模块ISO15693协议操作类
    RFID Module ISO15693 protocol class

    注意：
    1、使用前请确认您的机器已安装此模块。
    2、要正常使用模块需要在\libs\armeabi\目录放置libDeviceAPI.so文件
    3、在操作设备前需要调用 init() 打开设备，使用完后调用 free() 关闭设备
    Note: ? * 1, Please confirm that your machine has installed this module before use.
    ? * 2, For the normal use of the module need to place the libDeviceAPI.so file under below pathto \ libs \ armeabi \ directory.
    ? * 3, Before operation, you need to call open the device, use the call after the to close the device.

    作者:
    liuruifeng
